      • isFirstSensEventReceived

        public boolean isFirstSensEventReceived()
        True if the Sensor received its first sensor event and the sensormode of the received event is != null. Used during initialization process -> Only if the first sensor event was received it is assumed that the sensor is ready.
        Returns:
        true if the first sensor data was received else false
